NK013(pa)008:0: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK013(pa)008:15: h'u l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK013(pa)008:17: t+r+aam m+aa le sa ma ya hoh h+r+aim h+aa h'u pad+ma pra da ma /
NK013(pa)008:21: mee d+h+aa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)008:23: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)008:25: h'u sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)008:26: bam d+ai pa su gi ri /
NK013(pa)008:27: m+aum sh+r+ai am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)008:29: byed po yab yum dang thub drug la /
NK013(pa)008:31: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta +aah mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)008:32: mu ne h'u trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK013(pa)008:37: sgo ba yab yum brgyad la /
NK013(pa)008:39: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)008:41: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa li ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)008:43: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h'u phata /
NK013(pa)008:45: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai ni h'u phata /
